        Outdoor furniture - adjustable deckchair - General Requirements for Safety - Mechanical tests and specifications</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Note that deckchairs complying with version 2004 of NF D 61-062 can still be placed in the market until one year after the notice publication (February 5, 2017). Also, other standards for deckchairs or transatlantic chairs are still required to satisfy the Decree No. 99-777.</p>
